---
const stats = [
    { value: "767%", label: "increase in volunteer signups", sub: "in their first month" },
    { value: "90%", label: "reduction in admin burden", sub: "Staff free to focus on mission" },
    { value: "125", label: "touchpoints automated", sub: "No staff needed" },
    { value: "2×", label: "conversation volume", sub: "Across every channel" }
];
---

<section id="results" class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-emerald-800 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="fade-in">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <span class="text-emerald-200 font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide uppercase">Real Results — Austin Angels</span>
                <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-white mt-3">
                    From 3 to 26 volunteers in their first month<br /><span class="text-emerald-400">— with <span class="font-extrabold">zero new staff</span>.</span>
                </h2>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in" style="transition-delay: 100ms">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-8 mb-16 md:mb-24 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                {stats.map((stat) => (
                    <div class="text-center p-4 md:p-6">
                        <div class="font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">{stat.value}</div>
                        <div class="text-emerald-200 text-sm md:text-base">{stat.label}</div>
                        <div class="text-emerald-400/60 text-xs mt-1">{stat.sub}</div>
                    </div>
                ))}
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in" style="transition-delay: 200ms">
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-16">
                <div class="relative order-2 lg:order-1">
                    <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8">
                        <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-emerald-200 mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <p class="text-white text-xl lg:text-2xl font-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            In under a month, MyRecruiter brought in <span class="font-semibold text-emerald-400">more new volunteer leads than we'd typically see in a quarter</span>. These weren't just form fills — they were engaged, informed, and ready to get started.
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white/20 flex items-center justify-center">
                                <span class="text-white font-semibold">TR</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-white font-semibold">Tracy Randall</div>
                                <div class="text-emerald-200 text-sm">Executive Director, Austin Angels</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-xl">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                            <!-- Austin Angels Logo SVG -->
                            <svg class="h-10 w-auto" viewBox="0 0 200 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="25" fill="#50C878"/>
                                <path d="M30 15 L35 35 L25 35 Z" fill="white"/>
                                <text x="65" y="38" font-family="Plus Jakarta Sans, sans-serif" font-size="20" font-weight="600" fill="#1e293b">Austin Angels</text>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
                            Austin Angels supports foster families through mentorship, practical help, and community. Before MyRecruiter, their small team was stretched thin — trying to answer questions, onboard volunteers, and manage inquiries across channels.
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Foster Care</span>
                            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Austin, TX</span>
                            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">5-person team</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="fade-in text-center" style="transition-delay: 300ms">
            <a href="demo.html" class="inline-flex items-center flex-wrap text-emerald-200 hover:text-white font-medium text-lg transition-colors group">
                See what MyRecruiter could do for your&nbsp;
                <span class="whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                    organization
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
                    </svg>
                </span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
